# AI Development Rules for Olama School Weekly Plan (Eval 02)

- Do not perform a full-repository scan unless explicitly requested.
- When refactoring modules from the Core, only load the specific class file being moved and its corresponding entry point in the Core.
- Always prioritize RTL/Arabic compatibility when suggesting UI changes.
- **Token Saver**: Many files in this plugin are extremely large (e.g., `class-admin.php` is 245KB+). NEVER read these entire files. Always use `grep_search` to find relevant sections first, then use `view_file` with `StartLine` and `EndLine` to read only the specific code blocks needed for the task.
- Maintain consistency with the existing WordPress plugin architecture and coding standards.
- Ensure all weekly plan analysis and reporting features account for cumulative curriculum coverage as previously implemented.
